{"name":"Spirit Burn","permission":{"default":0,"qbUuGvCaFbrkiBWc":3},"type":"talent","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>You ignite your soul with the power of your bonds, and, converting that power into</p>\n<p>supernatural energy, you transcend reality.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>[Physical Transcendence]</strong> Bond # ①~③</p>\n<p>Unique Effect. Use before a check. The target may increase the number of dice for their [Roll] by 1 to 3. After the [Roll], the target rolls the same number of dice they added to the [Roll], and loses that amount of {Crest}. This effect may be used for each time a check is made. Although the increased dice may be [Influenced], if the user receives a reroll effect, the increased dice are lost.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>[Vital Ignition] </strong>Bond # ④~⑥</p>\n<p>Unique Effect. Use at any time. The target gains [Remove: Downed], sets their {HP} to be equal with their {Strength}, and then after that, loses 2d6 {Crest}. This effect may only be</p>\n<p>used once per combat.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>[Concept Destruction]</strong> Bond # ⑦</p>\n<p>Use On Damage Calculation. The target gains +1d6 to [Rank], and then after that, loses 2d6 {Crest}. This effect may be used each time [Damage Calculation] is performed.</p>","talentType":"COMMON","className":"","classType":"-","condition":"-","timing":"Unique","range":"User","target":"User","cost":"None","effect":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"Di4k73w8EYdi7c5b"}
{"_id":"sVtTn1n1W9CAcNce","name":"Spirit Barrier","permission":{"default":0,"qbUuGvCaFbrkiBWc":3},"type":"talent","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>By erecting a Spirit Barrier, you create an alternate space within a moment of a time, and instantly arm yourself with concealed equipment.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Unique Effect. When you gain &laquo;Spirit Barrier&raquo;, your [Stored] and [Equipped] [Items] and [Gold] can be kept continually hidden. Also, when you declare &laquo;Spirit Barrier&raquo;, or when you are declared as a target of another &laquo;Spirit Barrier&raquo;, your [Stored] [Items] can be freely [Equipped].&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>If you receive a Coup de Grace while within a &laquo;Spirit Barrier&raquo;, instead of becoming [Dead], you gain [Shift: Taken Out] instead. This &laquo;Latent Trait&raquo; does not expend your [Start] timing, and may only be used once per combat (or scene).</p>","talentType":"COMMON","className":"","classType":"-","condition":"-","timing":"Start","range":"Combat Zone","target":"Combat Zone","cost":"None","effect":"","class":""},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
